CalculatedMeasure.name: Access To Exercise Opportunities
CalculatedMeasure.Annotation: Percentage of population with adequate access to locations for physical activity
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([State Access to exercise opportunities]) THEN [State Access to exercise opportunities] ELSE [County Access to exercise opportunities] END

CalculatedMeasure.name: Access To Exercise Opportunities CI Low
CalculatedMeasure.Formula: CASE WHEN ISNOTNULL([mea_state_cilow Access to exercise opportunities]) THEN [mea_state_cilow Access to exercise opportunities] ELSE [mea_county_cilow Access to exercise opportunities] END
